 Pu compounds. The results of our calculations show that both spin-orbit\ncoupling and exchange interaction terms in the Hamiltonian must be treated in a\ngeneral matrix form for Pu and its compounds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Dec 2004 10:45:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 21 Jan 2005 08:08:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
